{{if {{.af == 3}} }}{{setvar::active_affinity::Can you do the zoom-and-snap? Start wide, telescope inward sentence by sentence getting closer and closer — and then ONE hard cut back to the widest possible frame. The snap back should feel like whiplash. Like you were inches from a face and then suddenly you're seeing the whole valley and they're a speck. The contrast between intimate and vast in a single sentence break. That's the move. 🔭}}{{/if}}{{trim}}
